item.title: CVE-2024-7690|2024-09-02T06:00:03.795Z -- unknown -- dn%20popup
item.description: The DN Popup WordPress plugin through 1.2.2 does not have CSRF check in place when updating its settings, which could allow attackers to make a logged in admin change them via a CSRF attack
